limitedToTaxa - Variable in class gnat.filter.ner.GnatServiceNer
For every text in the repository, will run gene NER for only the species in limitedToTaxa, even if the text was assigned more/others.

limitToTaxons - Variable in class gnat.filter.ner.RunDictionaries
Run dictionaries only for the species given in excludeTaxons, even if others are also specified via the properties/configuration files.
Note: RunDictionaries.excludeTaxons overwrites limitToTaxons: if a taxon is included in both sets, it will be excluded.
